OL,4,CIan Wright: Penalty-takers should be
OL,5,Cdecided before the game
OL,6, Former Arsenal striker Ian Wright says
OL,7, penalty-takers "need to be decided
OL,8, before the game".
OL,10,FWright, who scored 20 penalties in his
OL,11,FGunners career, said it was
OL,12,F"indecisive" for managers not to have
OL,13,Fone designated taker.
OL,15,F"I was the penalty-taker. If I missed
OL,16,Ftwo, then Dennis Bergkamp would be the
OL,17,Fpenalty-taker," Wright told BBC Radio 5
OL,18,FLive's Monday Night Club.
OL,20,FWright said he used to take 25
OL,21,Fpenalties after training to practise.
